            "question": "Are there toll roads beyond the standard vignette?",
            "question_de": "Gibt es Mautstraßen zusätzlich zur Standard-Vignette?",
            "answer": "Yes. Some Alpine tunnels and special routes require separate tolls in addition to the vignette. Tyrol and Salzburg routes are common examples—check your route before you travel.",
            "answer_de": "Ja. Einige Alpentunnel und Sonderstrecken erfordern zusätzliche Maut neben der Vignette—besonders in Tirol und Salzburg. Route vorab prüfen.",
