            "id": "speed-limits",
            "category": "speed_limits",
            "question": "What are the standard speed limits in Austria?",
            "question_de": "Welche Tempolimits gelten in Österreich?",
            "answer": "Unless signed otherwise, typical limits are 50 km/h in urban areas, 100 km/h on rural roads, and 130 km/h on motorways. Always follow posted signs—they override general limits.",
            "answer_de": "Typische Limits: 50 km/h innerorts, 100 km/h außerorts, 130 km/h auf Autobahnen—sofern nicht anders ausgeschildert. Schilder haben Vorrang.",
