            "question": "When are snow chains required?",
            "question_de": "Wann sind Schneeketten Pflicht?",
            "answer": "Snow chains may be mandatory on signed Alpine routes during winter conditions, even if winter tyres are fitted. Carry chains when driving mountain passes, especially in Tyrol.",
